{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "electronics-mart-api-2026",
    "name": "Electronics Mart API Collection",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Electronics Mart e-commerce platform with comprehensive payment processing.\n\n## üöÄ Features\n- **Authentication System**: Customer registration, login, email verification\n- **Product Management**: Browse products and categories\n- **Shopping Cart**: Add, update, remove items\n- **Order Processing**: Complete checkout with multiple payment methods\n- **Payment Methods**: Card payments, PayPal, and Bank transfers\n\n## üí≥ Payment Processing\n\n### Card Payments\n- Requires `card_number` and `card_holder_name`\n- Card numbers are masked in responses (last 4 digits only)\n- Automatic payment processing and order confirmation\n\n### PayPal Payments\n- Requires `paypal_username` (email or username)\n- Automatic payment processing and order confirmation\n\n### Bank Transfers\n- No additional fields required\n- Orders remain in 'processing' status until manual confirmation\n\n## üîí Security\n- All API endpoints require authentication (except public browsing)\n- Card numbers are never stored in full (masked after processing)\n- Secure token-based authentication\n- Input validation and error handling\n\n## üìã Usage\n1. **Setup**: Set `base_url` variable to your API endpoint\n2. **Authenticate**: Register/login to get auth token\n3. **Browse**: View products and categories\n4. **Shop**: Add items to cart\n5. **Checkout**: Create order with payment details\n\n## üõ†Ô∏è Environment Variables\n- `base_url`: Your API base URL (e.g., http://localhost:8000/api)\n- `auth_token`: Authentication token (auto-set after login)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "electronics-mart"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "üìñ Payment Documentation",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Payment Methods Overview",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/test",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "test"
              ]
            },
            "description": "# Payment Methods Overview\n\nThe Electronics Mart API supports three payment methods for order processing:\n\n## üí≥ Card Payments\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- `payment_method`: \"card\"\n- `card_number`: Full card number (16-19 digits)\n- `card_holder_name`: Name on the card\n\n**Security:**\n- Card numbers are immediately masked after processing\n- Only last 4 digits stored and returned in responses\n- Format: \"**** **** **** 1234\"\n\n**Processing:**\n- Automatic payment processing\n- Order status set to \"confirmed\"\n- Payment status set to \"completed\"\n\n## üí∞ PayPal Payments\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- `payment_method`: \"paypal\"\n- `paypal_username`: PayPal email or username\n\n**Processing:**\n- Automatic payment processing\n- Order status set to \"confirmed\"\n- Payment status set to \"completed\"\n\n## üè¶ Bank Transfer\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- `payment_method`: \"bank_transfer\"\n\n**Processing:**\n- Manual payment confirmation required\n- Order status remains \"processing\"\n- Payment status remains \"pending\"\n\n## üìã Common Order Fields\n\nAll payment methods require these shipping fields:\n- `shipping_name`: Recipient name\n- `shipping_email`: Recipient email\n- `shipping_phone`: Phone number (optional)\n- `shipping_address`: Street address\n- `shipping_city`: City\n- `shipping_state`: State/Province\n- `shipping_postal_code`: ZIP/Postal code\n- `shipping_country`: Country\n- `notes`: Order notes (optional)\n\n## ‚úÖ Validation Rules\n\n- Card payments: `card_number` and `card_holder_name` are required\n- PayPal payments: `paypal_username` is required\n- Bank transfers: No additional fields required\n- Missing required fields return 422 validation errors\n\n## üì§ Response Format\n\nSuccessful orders return:\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Order placed successfully\",\n  \"order\": { /* order details */ },\n  \"payment_status\": \"completed|pending\",\n  \"payment_method\": \"card|paypal|bank_transfer\",\n  \"payment_details\": {\n    \"card_last_four\": \"1234\", // for card payments\n    \"card_holder_name\": \"John Doe\", // for card payments\n    \"paypal_username\": \"user@paypal.com\" // for PayPal payments\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
